# Installation of GHC 8.4.4

## Installation Script

~~~
# get distribution   
cd $HOME/Downloads  
wget https://downloads.haskell.org/~ghc/8.4.4/ghc-8.4.4-x86_64-deb8-linux.tar.xz

tar xvfJ ghc-8.4.4-x86_64-deb8-linux.tar.xz

cd ghc-8.4.4 

# install  
mkdir $HOME/Software/ghc-8.4.4  

./configure --prefix=$HOME/Software/ghc-8.4.4  
make install

# cleanup: remove temporary files  
cd ..  
rm -rfv ghc-8.4.4*
~~~

## Activation Script

~~~
switchghc 8.4.4 
~~~